Implementation and Testing Design

1. Draw a tank
	- Does it look like a tank?
	- Can I draw it anywhere on the screen?
	- Can I turn it to any heading?
	- Does it leave a trail or disappear or other bad things when I am "moving" it?

2. Move that tank with the keyboard
	- ...

General structure:

A. Thing I'm implementing
	- Criteria to be sure that this thing works